attributes.Long form description: The student must detach the lens; he accidentally detaches the cover; the instructor shows him how to detach it; he makes the same mistake and detaches the cover; The instructor instructs him to grab the lens from the bottom and rotate it, but the student grabs it from the top; the teacher corrects him, and he detaches the lens with difficulty; he then puts back the lens and the two parts of the cover; The next instruction is to turn on and off the camera, which the student does easily. The next step is to exchange the battery; the student opens a door that is not the battery door; the teacher corrects him and finds the battery door; he exchanges it and does the same with the SD card.
